sentence.text: Fasting serum tumor necrosis factor (negative regulation of transcription by RNA polymerase II)-like antigen 1A (TL1A) and its receptor death receptor 3 (DR3), negative regulation of axon extension-B (reticulon 4B) and its receptor dolichyl diphosphate biosynthetic process, high-sensitivity C-reactive protein (hsCRP), A disintegrin and metalloproteinase with thrombospondin motifs (ADAMTS) 1, 4, 5 and interleukin (IL) 6 levels were determined.
